title: Iced Trapple By Killer Fruits Vapetasia
description: You can get anything by asking! Fruit lovers can rejoice as Vapetasia, the company that created the Killer Custard line, has given us access to their fruit collection, Killer Fruits! A daily apple? Why not three? A flavorful concoction of red, green, and golden apples combined with menthol will leave you with a refreshing taste of delectable fruit.
